{
  "stem": "17299.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But, but when the Germans counted, to find out one had escaped.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So they searched through the houses and they found this one and two other Jews in a basement.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They marched them on the [NON-ENGLISH] and [?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Krauzer ?] shot all three.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And one SS man also got killed in the firing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I watched that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there was even a third ghetto, a small part, where close to 300 women were-- Latvian women.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Hope that the Germans would lose the war.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But at the same time, we were under no illusion.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We said, they may kill us all before.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There were-- we had no change in the rations.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was not enough.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And you had to get illegal food to-- to sustain.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now-- most of the army kommandos where the Jews were were giving soup to the Jews.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When I found out, from my sister-in-law, that the Jews who worked in the motor pool for the Gestapo-- we are supposed to be separated from the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she told me, get out of that work kommando.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I took my bread ration to a Dr.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Frankenbash, ?] who was a [? group ?] doctor from Dusseldorf, I gave him my ration and I asked him to give me a slip that I had a hernia.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because you had to be healthy to work in a motor pool.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Of course, that was very heavy work.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And it worked.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I was assigned to the army closing depot for two weeks, which was the worst work kommando in the ghetto, but I could care less.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was assigned to the army bakery.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, wait a minute, no-- I became group leader of a work kommando-- [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was the army was collecting scrap metal for recycling in Germany.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
